_sText:
I created this prefab for one of my zombie maps, it contains 3 ak47's 2 duel elites, 3 sg552, 10 He grenades, 3 xm1014, 4 deagles and 3 m249, the doors you see on the front are all seperate and should open upwards on touch (E). Please feel free to use this and mod it to your own specifications. Just simply extract it to your prefab folder in:
C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\(yoursteamname)\sourcesdk\bin\prefabs. Enjoy

Please rate and give hints.
